OL,4,Cwith 'life-changing injury' following
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FTwo men have been arrested after a
OL,8,FWelsh footballer suffered a "life-
OL,9,Fchanging injury" when his knee was
OL,10,Fbroken in an alleged attack following
OL,11,Fa weekend match in Cardiff.
OL,13,FA 28-year-old man from Trowbridge and
OL,14,Fa 22-year-old man from Llanrumney have
OL,15,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of assault
OL,16,Fand violent disorder following a
OL,17,Ffootball match in Llanrumney on
OL,18,FSaturday, 12 October.
