OL,7,FThe two men remain in police custody
OL,8,Fand the investigation is ongoing,
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police has confirmed.
OL,11,FOne of the men injured in the attack,
OL,12,FJoel Collins, 32, is undergoing knee
OL,13,Fsurgery following the incident.
OL,15,FMr Collins' team, Avenue Hotspur FC `
OL,16,Fwhich is based in Ely ` had lost 3-1
OL,17,Fin a Cardiff and District Football
OL,18,FLeague division one match to
OL,19,FLlanrumney Athletic at the Eastern
OL,20,FLeisure Centre in Llanrumney before
OL,21,Fthe incident.
